   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VrS15.2 Var. a (mss. 2030, 2101, 2106, 2109, 5020):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>yeŋ́hē mē ... jasāi vaṇtā</em> frāgām ud ǰām ō ī war ī grih ī barsom burdan ud rāspīg ēsm pad <em>vaṇtā</em> ō ī ātaxš dādan harw gyāg-ē kē bēd kunišn <em>xšaθrəm vairīm bāgəm aibī.bairištəm</em>.</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At <em>yeŋ́hē mē ... jasāi vaṇtā</em> (the <em>zōt</em>) should bring the <em>frāgām</em> and the <em>ǰām</em> towards the knot of the <em>barsom</em> and, at
            <em>vaṇtā</em>, the <em>rāspīg</em> should give <em>ēsm</em> to the fire. At each passage that is so, he has to do it."</ab>
         
         <ab>VrS15.2 Var. b (mss. 2010, 4040):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>vohū xšaϑrəm vairīm bāgəm aibībairištəm</em> frāgām ud ǰām ō ī war ī grih ī barsom burdan rāspīg ēsm pad ātaxš nihādan harw gyāg kū bēd kunišn</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At <em>vohū xšaϑrəm vairīm bāgəm aibībairištəm</em> he should bring the <em>frāgām</em> and the <em>ǰām</em> towards the knot of the <em>barsom</em>. 
            The <em>rāspīg</em> should put <em>ēsm</em> into the fire. Every time when it happens (that this is recited), he has to do it."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
